  <brief_title>Proposal and Clinical Evaluation of a Comprehensive Airway Exam Score</brief_title>
  <official_title>The &quot;KU Score&quot;: Proposal and Clinical Evaluation of a Comprehensive Airway Exam Score; an Observational Study</official_title>
